            <h3>St. Carlo Acutis - The Cyber Apostle</h3>
            <p>Carlo Acutis was an Italian teenager known for his deep love of the Eucharist and his ability to use technology to spread the faith. Despite his young age, he created a website documenting Eucharistic miracles worldwide.</p>
